{"type": "article", "id": 21608, "title": "“dent”by skrivo", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-01T01:00:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 30, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606161352iA9PRNzrFklgjp2M.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>这是一组彩色的陶瓷灯，来自意大利的设计工作室skrivo。他们先通过拉坯做成圆形的灯罩，然后挤捏成一个凹形，使得最下面的口依然是圆形的，而上面却形成了一种折纸感，有一种清新的童趣。从不同角度看这款灯能有不同的阴影变化，横插在其中的实木可以让灯保持平衡并固定灯泡，<a href=\"http://www.skrivo.com/#/dent/\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606161349tg3Wucfq87SzMn1r.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.84352078\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n        \r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606161349XidcQWKRJ2eIgyTx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.3594132\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n        \r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606161350EfZVqvunFSWw5O7a.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n        \r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606161350JMWtGUZjswQY5eIi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.33374083\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n        \r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606161351mBfKMcWCZR5Dx6hq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.33251834\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n        \r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n\n"}